db and phpmyadmin: docker compose up 
backend: node index.js
frontend: npm run dev

API:
- POST /api/sync/prices
  body: { "start": "ISO-8601 UTC", "end": "ISO-8601 UTC", "location": "EE|LV|FI" }
  defaults: start/end = current UTC day range, location = EE
  errors: { "error": "PRICE_API_UNAVAILABLE" } when external API is unavailable
- GET /api/readings?start=...&end=...&location=EE|LV|FI
  - location supports one or many values (e.g. `location=EE` or `location=EE,LV,FI`)
